rows.label: tlk000016_msg0001
rows.name:
Orara heard, mo!
You're going to Luxuria, Mo-mo?

rows.label: tlk000016_msg0005
rows.name:
The Acedian captain is depressed
about Fan-sama and can't steer properly...

rows.label: tlk000016_msg0006
rows.name:
So Orara was chosen for the job, mo!
I've never been there before, but I'll do
my best to get us there somehow, mo!

rows.label: tlk000016_msg0007
rows.name:
Well, there's someone who looks like
a Luxurian prince with you, so it'll
probably be fine, mo.

rows.label: tlk000016_msg0008
rows.name:
I understand you need to mentally prepare
yourselves to go to Luxuria, mo.

rows.label: tlk000016_msg0009
rows.name: Orara can wait here for as long as you need, mo.
